---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Experience | Aadit Agrawal">
    <section id="experience" class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="label-text">EXPERIENCE</h2>
            <div class="line"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="exp-list">
            <article class="exp-card">
                <div class="exp-header">
                    <h3>
                        Lead Research Engineer <span class="exp-at"
                            >@ CASIR, School of Computing, MAHE</span>
                    </h3>
                    <span class="label-text font-mono">MAY 2025-PRES</span>
                </div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Engineered an LLM-powered industrial protocol translator
                        parsing IEC 61131-3 to IEC 61499, cutting
                        PLC migration timelines for external manufacturing
                        clients.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Architected a massive on-premise production cluster
                        running heavy AI workloads, load-balancing traffic
                        across varied architectures (ARM64 Apple Silicon and
                        CUDA Blackwells).
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Deployed an edge-compute computer vision pipeline onto
                        NVIDIA Jetson hardware flying on DJI drones, sustaining
                        30 fps inference directly on the embedded board via
                        RTMP.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Built an end-to-end full-stack agentic RAG pipeline
                        processing 2000+ structured layouts via custom OCR
                        tools.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="exp-card">
                <div class="exp-header">
                    <h3>
                        Platform Engineer <span class="exp-at"
                            >@ <a href="https://rossmanngroup.com"
                                >Rossmann New Media 2 Inc.</a
                            ></span>
                    </h3>
                    <span class="label-text font-mono">JAN 2026—PRES</span>
                </div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Led a full-stack migration from legacy
                        WordPress to a modern React/Next.js ecosystem.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Redesigned the UI for true cross-device responsiveness,
                        improving core web vitals and overall LCP by 60%+.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Executed a technical SEO overhaul by analyzing
                        and mapping data recovery search patterns, moving
                        keyword rankings into the top 5.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="exp-card">
                <div class="exp-header">
                    <h3>
                        DevOps Engineer <span class="exp-at"
                            >@ Rasen AI (formerly Pixa AI), Bengaluru</span>
                    </h3>
                    <span class="label-text font-mono">DEC 2025</span>
                </div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Focused purely on infrastructure-as-code and
                        reliability, provisioning varied compute nodes
                        (H100/H200/B200) tailored for heavy TTS/STT fine-tuning
                        operations.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Designed and implemented robust automated CI/CD
                        pipelines guaranteeing 99.5% deployment success across
                        consecutive API releases.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="exp-card">
                <div class="exp-header">
                    <h3>
                        Founding President <span class="exp-at"
                            >@ <a href="https://theprism.fyi"
                                >PRISM - Computing & AI Club, MAHE</a
                            ></span>
                    </h3>
                    <span class="label-text font-mono">JAN 2026—PRES</span>
                </div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Founded and manage an interdisciplinary collective of
                        150+ members focused on pushing the envelope across Web
                        Development, embedded IoT, DevOps and Applied AI.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Act as a technical bridge by serving on MAHE's Academic
                        Advisory Board, helping adapt curricula to modern tech
                        stacks.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="exp-card">
                <div class="exp-header">
                    <h3>
                        Infrastructure Lead <span class="exp-at"
                            >@ MIST (Cybersecurity Club)</span>
                    </h3>
                    <span class="label-text font-mono">OCT 2023-JUN 2025</span>
                </div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Architected a resilient, dynamic CTF web platform
                        supporting 300+ concurrent players, sustaining 100%
                        uptime across 3 high-load events.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Optimized cloud configurations and resource
                        limits, reducing operational overhead by
                        80%.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding-left: var(--space-sm);
    }

    li {
        position: relative;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding-left: var(--space-md);
    }

    li::before {
        content: "▪";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: var(--text-disabled);
        font-size: 12px;
    }
</style>
